iter  Tom Cruisewill reportedly have a starring role in the Paris 2024 Olympic Games' Aug. 11 closing ceremony, when he may skydive to the Hollywood Sign during the orchestrated handoff to Los Angeles for the 2028 Olympiad.\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L._Frank_Baum\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.0569521287013943e-13, \"text\": \"Baum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L._Frank_Baum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L._Frank_Baum\"}, {\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood Sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.217920223707722e-14, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toTMZ, the stuntwas quietly shotin March.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise has attended the Paris games, including for the women's gymnastics qualifiers as well as swimming competitions.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999533884, \"rank\": 4.6535462337699664e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's awesome,\\\" hetoldReuters.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Great stories, great athletes.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's incredible what they have to do, the sense of accomplishment.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Related StoriesMovies'Spartacus: House of Ashur' Creator, Star Talk Pushing Boundaries of Sex and Violence, Intimacy Coordinators and Not Changing the Written WordMovies\\\"The Villagers Were the Key to Making This Film Happen\\\": 'THR Presents' Q&A With 'Sun Never Again' Director David Jovanovic  Production company Fulwell 73 - co-run by James Corden and known for Hulu'sThe Kardashiansas well as Adele's 2021 CBS specialOne Night Only, which took place at the iconic Griffith Observatory - is behind the L.A. segment, which will mix prerecorded and live elements.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Corden\", \"score\": 0.9999916088060761, \"rank\": 8.391264335441763e-06, \"text\": \"James Corden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Corden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Corden\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Griffith_Observatory\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Griffith Observatory\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Griffith_Observatory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Griffith_Observatory\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2043100931057763e-12, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hollywood Reporterhas learned that an early plan involved a large party at Will Rogers State Beach, where the handoff of the Olympic flag would occur.\", 